dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3222346b877e53f37e68acc15defb0995b9d3215","tid":887104,"uid":211592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de9fc6d8033afb84de6f95b19d288400426a8691","tid":887104,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:16:39.000Z","msg":"我知宜家咩時勢 🤦🏻&zwj;♂️thx師兄意見"},{"pid":"737149505359cd9c10fe85d85c53d86488120f86","tid":887104,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T21:33:42.000Z","msg":"你有同你老母講出重點咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你不如講裝修間屋好過 無論幾迫<br />\n都間多間房出黎比你用咪搞撚掂囉<br />\n搞咁多野 又買樓又乜乜乜<br />\n如果你老母裝修都唔肯既<br />\n就算鳩數啦"}]}